'''Qwasi Blay Jnr.''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Gana]] .  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri firime ''Adoma'' na ''Grilled'' . Yagaragaye muri firime cumi neshanu na seri enye za TV. 

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Yavukiye muri [[Gana]] nk'umwana wa gatatu mu muryango ufite barumuna be batanu: abagabo bane n'umugore. Yarangije amashuri abanza n'ayisumbuye muri Great Lamptey Mills. Hanyuma yakomereje amashuri muri Aburi Secondary Technical (SHS). Amashuri makuru yayize muri kaminuza ya tekinike ya Koforidua ahabwa impamyabumenyi ihanitse (HND) mu kugura no gutanga.  

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina mu 2016 akiri umwana, agaragara muri ''Gray Dust'', ''Grilled'', na serial ''Deju Vu'' .  Yahawe Best Entertainment Male honor at the tertiary level and best male entertainment act at the maiden edition of the Social Media Entertainment awards.  Nyuma yaje gutorwa nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu mwanya wa mbere mu nshuro ya 9 ya [[Gana]] Movie Awards kubera uruhare muri filime ''Adoma'' .    

